Four Seasons to Operate Southern Cross Care Homes, FT Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-03T20:30:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-03/four-seasons-to-operate-southern-cross-care-homes-ft-reports.html
Four Seasons Healthcare Group Ltd.,
owner of 45 care homes leased to  Southern Cross  Healthcare Plc,
will take over the running of the homes Southern Cross has
earmarked for possible closure, the Financial Times reported,
citing an interview with Chief Executive Officer Peter Calveley.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 